contentrichtext.text: {{italic title}}<!-- This article was auto-generated by [[User:Polbot]]. --> {{Taxobox | name = Xenorhina bouwensi | image = | status = LC | status_system = IUCN3.1 | regnum = [[Animalia]] | phylum = [[Chordata]] | classis = [[Amphibia]] | ordo = [[Frog|Anura]] | familia = [[Microhylidae]] | genus = ''[[Xenorhina]]'' | species = '''''X. bouwensi''''' | binomial = ''Xenorhina bouwensi'' | binomial_authority = (Witte, 1930) | synonyms = }} '''''Xenorhina bouwensi''''' is a species of [[frog]] in the [[Microhylidae]] family.
